---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<section class="bg-[#080b12] py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div
      class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-[linear-gradient(135deg,rgb(16_24_39_/_0.92),rgb(8_11_18_/_0.92))] p-8 shadow-[0_1.5rem_5rem_rgb(0_0_0_/_0.24)] sm:p-10 lg:p-12"
    >
      <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.28fr_1fr] lg:items-center">
        <div
          class="flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-cyan-300/10 text-cyan-200 ring-1 ring-white/10"
        >
          <Icon name="tabler:shield-check" class="h-8 w-8" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-200">安全与运营</p>
          <h2 class="mt-4 max-w-4xl text-3xl font-semibold tracking-normal text-white sm:text-4xl">
            接入方案会同时考虑安全、支付数据保护和澳洲本地运营要求。
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-base leading-8 text-slate-400">
            我们协助客户在设备接入、SDK 集成、交易流程和上线部署中建立更清晰、更可靠的本地化实施路径。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
